{"tid":2449802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跟著空投大師凱爾巴斯Kyle Bass分析一下阿里巴巴的賬本","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T03:26:00.000Z","uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5df6dd582f18e91f7d5d0ae860046f1e90a04180","tid":2449802,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:08:03.000Z","msg":"現在，讓我們跟著空投大師凱爾巴斯Kyle Bass分析一下阿里巴巴的賬本。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/agmDHJce2wk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FagmDHJce2wk&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=63a1bde4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/agmDHJce2wk</a><br />\n<br />\n一位「神秘客戶」雇傭了視頻中的嘉賓史蒂夫對幾大中國在美上市企業進行審計。他們毫不意外地發現了阿里存在大量的造假。問題既是出在審計規則上，也出在企業 自身上。更重要的是，它通過VIE架構隱藏了阿里真正的所有人。<br />\n<br />\n凱爾巴斯在視頻中風趣的表示，如果你是阿里巴巴股票持有人，你應該派 特種部隊去把馬雲揪出來，讓他對阿里的財務做個交代。在幾個中國企業被踢出美國證券市 場之後，真正的大鰐阿里巴巴會不會是下一個？"},{"pid":"4370ebc8cb18a4efbe61e272ddd38acb3452a8e4","tid":2449802,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:09:16.000Z","msg":"凱爾&middot;巴斯（Kyle Bass)<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%87%AF%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2587%25AF%25E5%25B0%2594%25C2%25B7%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%2596%25AF&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=c552956a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%87%AF%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%B7%B4%E6%96%AF</a>"},{"pid":"42e0d20544d83202af636038ff609e56f8f668f9","tid":2449802,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:09:49.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"2e0bfe45c944f8936a8a5c8497a5c73463c16bd5","tid":2449802,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/face